tourBios.curYrHigh: Earned conditional status on PGA TOUR Latinoamérica with a T11 finish at the Mazatlán, Mexico Q-School in January.
tourBios.carHigh: Prior to joining PGA TOUR Latinoamérica he played on the Golden State Tour and the EGolf Tour.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Played college golf at Loyola Marymount University, where he collected four individual wins.
tourBios.personal: His brother, Tucker, plays baseball in college... If not a professional golfer says he would be a pilot... The San Diego Padres and Chargers are his favorite professional teams... Loves Korean food... Likes to wear "funky" socks... His favorite golf course to play is the Los Angeles Country Club... His father, Jordan Spieth and Payne Stewart would round out his dream foursome.
